ARM: tegra: Add OF_DEV_AUXDATA for sflash driver in board dt

Add OF_DEV_AUXDATA for sflash controller driver for Tegra20
board dt files.
Set the parent clock of sflash controller to PLLP and configure
clock to 20MHz.

